### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks

### Get a task by ID 
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks/68ed22e52bb0c04f4b4cbe9a

### Create a task
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish homework",
  "description": "Math and Science tasks",
  "completed": false
}

### Update a task by ID (replace {id})
PUT http://localhost:8080/tasks/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish homework updated",
  "description": "Math, Science, and English tasks",
  "completed": true
}

### Delete a task by ID (replace {id})
DELETE http://localhost:8080/tasks/{id}

